Goblin Scanner v4 (Pantheon Stack)

We combine four layers of signals.

1️⃣ Momentum Layer

Classic breakout indicators.

Signals:
	•	price within 10% of 20-day high
	•	volume >150% normal
	•	relative strength vs market

These detect early acceleration.

⸻

2️⃣ Volatility Layer

The volatility compression → expansion signal.

Before large runs:

price range gets tight
volatility drops
volume slowly rises

This is often called a volatility squeeze.

Many 5×–10× small-cap runs start here.

⸻

3️⃣ Narrative Layer

This is where the Pantheon lens is powerful.

Ask:

Is there a macro story pulling money in?

Current hot narratives:
	•	AI infrastructure
	•	semiconductors
	•	photonics
	•	defense tech
	•	satellite telecom
	•	nuclear / energy

Stocks tied to big capital flows move hardest.

⸻

4️⃣ Sentiment Layer

This detects early crowd attention.

Signals:
	•	Reddit / WSB mentions rising
	•	unusual options call activity
	•	analyst upgrades
	•	insider buying

Often:

smart money buys
→ online attention appears
→ retail piles in


⸻

Goblin Score System

Each stock gets points:

Signal	Points
momentum breakout	1
volume spike	1
volatility squeeze	1
near 52-week high	1
strong narrative	1
options activity	1
rising online attention	1

Maximum:

7 points

Interpretation:

0-2 = ignore
3-4 = watch
5-6 = trade candidate
7 = goblin rocket


